OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine end
OL,6,Fto the day, with plenty of warm
OL,7,Fsunshine. Staying dry with prolonged
OL,8,Fclear skies overnight. Winds will be
OL,9,Flight and variable. A warm night for
OL,10,Fmany.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA sunny start becoming cloudy
OL,13,Fwith chance of some isolated thundery
OL,14,Fshowers developing in the afternoon.
OL,15,FOvernight turns more settled with
OL,16,Fclearing skies. Temperatures remaining
OL,17,Fhigh.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
