OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FLargely bright and sunny on Wednesday
OL,7,Fand Thursday becoming cloudy on
OL,8,FFriday. Temperatures may start to
OL,9,Fdecrease from Thursday as it becomes
OL,10,Fbreezier, especially along the coast.
